        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Queen's Momentum",
          "description": "This unit gains 3 Charges and a Sleep Ward. Triggered both at the very start of the battle if this unit is on the battlefield, and when this unit enters the battlefield from reinforcements. If this unit would be defeated while it has any charges, this unit will consume 1 charge to survive with 1HP remaining instead. Other skills may also be affected by and may consume charges. A unit can store up to 3 charges.\n\nEach time this unit defeats an enemy with an attack, this unit will get another turn and gain 3 Charges.\n\n-Effects that influence TU order may interrupt the extra turn (e.g. Stuns targeting the lowest TU target)."
